    <span class="taxonomy"></span>
    <div class="content"><p>Here are some screen captures of the poster behind Tyrol in the produce market.   You can&#8217;t really read the words reliably, but in the first two lines, it really seems like the last word is &#8220;Cylon&#8221; &#8212; though there is some argument for &#8220;Colony&#8221;</p>

<p><img class=blogpic src=/files/cff.jpg></p>

<p>In the next set of 3 lines, I see</p>

<blockquote>
  <p>A Celebration/Discussion ?? 7??? and ch?????? in the (eyes?) of the community.</p>
